            <title><![CDATA[Persona 4 Revival and STRANGER THAN HEAVEN due out after April 1, 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/persona-4-revival-and-stranger-than-heaven-due-out-after-april-1-2026</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/persona-4-revival-and-stranger-than-heaven-due-out-after-april-1-2026.1224444/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div role="main">
  
  <article>

    
<header>

  <div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>2025 release not on the cards.</span>
      </p></div>

  

</header>  

<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p><a title="Companies > ATLUS [2,055 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atlus">ATLUS</a>‘ <em><a title="Games > Persona 4 Revival [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/persona-4-revival">Persona 4 Revival</a></em> and <a title="Companies > Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio [498 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega/ryu-ga-gotoku-studio">Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio</a>‘s <em><a title="Games > STRANGER THAN HEAVEN [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/stranger-than-heaven">STRANGER THAN HEAVEN</a></em> will launch in or after fiscal year 2027, which runs between April 1, 2026 on March 31, 2027, according to a <a href="https://www.segasammy.co.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/pdf/en/ir/20250618_Management_large_MTG_all_e.pdf" target="_blank">SEGA SAMMY Management Meeting 2025 presentation</a> published on June 18. <span id="more-975162"></span></p><p><em>Persona 4 Revival</em> was <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/persona-4-revival-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-and-pc">announced</a> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,783 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,448 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,551 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> (Steam, <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/persona-4-revival/9n40dk5n4ld4" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a>) earlier this month, with a teaser trailer showcasing “early development content.”</p><p><em>STRANGER THAN HEAVEN</em> was <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/12/sega-and-ryu-ga-gotoku-studio-announce-project-century">first announced</a> at The Game Awards 2024, but was officially titled with a new trailer <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/sega-and-ryu-ga-gotoku-studios-project-century-officially-titled-stranger-than-heaven">earlier this month</a>. Platforms have yet to be announced.</p></div>

        
    
  </article>
</div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/persona-4-revival-and-stranger-than-heaven-due-out-after-april-1-2026]]></content:encoded>
